FBIS4-5165 "dreas068_c_94014" FBIS-EAS-94-068 Daily Report 7 Apr 1994 North Korea Agreements Signed on Information Services Agreements Signed on Information Services With Laos SK0704132194 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1021 GMT 7 Apr 94 SK0704132194 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, April 7 (KCNA) -- An agreement on cooperation in information service was signed in Vientiane on March 31 between the Information Committee of the DPRK and the Ministry of Information and Culture of the Lao People's Democratic Republic. The agreement was signed by Yi Pong-hui, vice-chairman of the Information Committee of the DPRK, and Bouasy Chaleunsouk, first vice-minister of Information and Culture of Laos.
